value.0: This fine statue seems to have withstood the test of time, in spite of it sinking into the ground as the years march on. When it was first erected, the Aljana Warrens were probably a very pristine area.
This crate holds contains many mundane supplies. Only the occasional item is of any use or value.
This patch of mold seems ordinary at first, until faint changes in the air above the mold begin to mesmerize you...
